{"content": "I need to multiply 782 \u00d7 124 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 782\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 567 + 72 + 2 = 641\u2081\u2080\n- 124\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 1\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 81 + 18 + 4 = 103\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 641 \u00d7 103 = 66,023\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 66023 \u00f7 9 = 7336 r 7\n- 7336 \u00f7 9 = 815 r 1\n- 815 \u00f7 9 = 90 r 5\n- 90 \u00f7 9 = 10 r 0\n- 10 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 1\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **110517\u2089**\n\n110517", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 342}